beer.beer_description: An easy drinking beer developed by Dr Ian Davis and Cavalier Brewing to help raise awareness and funds for research into Motor Neuron Disease (MND). A crisp refreshing blonde ale, using quality all Australian ingredients. Summer saaz hops create the soft fruity aroma and slight bitterness. The presents light golden in clour with a mild malt flavour making it a perfectly balanced beer for any occasion
